sense.gloss: results of a scientific investigation, findings

sdata.j: 「↑自分↑↓じぶん↓の↑足↑↓あし↓が↑臭↑↓くさ↓いと↑思↑↓おも↓っている↑人↑↓ひと↓の↑足↑↓あし↓は↑臭↑↓くさ↓く、↑思↑↓おも↓っていない↑人↑↓ひと↓のは↑臭↑↓くさ↓くない」という↑研究↑↓|けんきゅう↓↑結果↑↓けっか|↓がある。
sdata.e: The conclusion reached by a study is "People who think their feet are smelly, have smelly feet; people who think they aren't, don't."
